==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unkingship
<hw>Un*king"ship</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality or condition of
being unkinged; abolition of monarchy.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Unkingship</qex> was proclaimed, and his majesty's statues
thrown down.</q> <rj><qau>Evelyn.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unkiss</ent>⟦br⟧
